de.adorsys.opba.protocol.api.dto.codes

Enum FieldCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<FieldCode>
      • de.adorsys.opba.protocol.api.dto.codes.FieldCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<FieldCode>

    public enum FieldCode
extends Enum<FieldCode>
    Represents what kind of input is expected/provided from/by user. For example protocol may want users' PSU_ID in order to create consent. This code is used to represent this.
